<h3 class="heading"><span class="type">Paragraph</span></h3>
<p>To find  <span class="process-math">\(c\)</span> is in this case, we utilize the fact that <span class="process-math">\(v(0)=19.6\text{.}\)</span>  Thus</p>
<div class="displaymath process-math" data-contains-math-knowls="">
\begin{equation*}
19.6=v(0)=-9.8(0)+c =c.
\end{equation*}
</div>
<p class="continuation">So our velocity is given by</p>
<div class="displaymath process-math" data-contains-math-knowls="">
\begin{equation*}
v=-9.8t+19.6.
\end{equation*}
</div>
<span class="incontext"><a href="section-3.html#p-34" class="internal">in-context</a></span>
</body>
